random.seed(42)
a = [getNextAddr()]
o1 = TestObj(a[0], [])
objs = [o1]
assert not o1._isReady()
doTicks(objs, 3.0, stopFunc=lambda : o1._isReady())
o1._printStatus()
assert o1._getLeader().address in a
assert o1._isReady()
o1.addValue(150)
o1.addValue(200)
doTicks(objs, 3.0, stopFunc=lambda : o1.getCounter() == 350)
assert o1._isReady()
assert o1.getCounter() == 350
o1._destroy()
